                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Idiomas:</strong> Espanol nativo, Ingles basico</p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Editores:</strong> Visual Studio Code, Android Studio</p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Lenguajes:</strong> TypeScript, JavaScript, PHP, HTML, CSS, Dart</p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Frameworks:</strong> Tailwind CSS, Bootstrap, Node.js</p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Bibliotecas:</strong> React, Express.js</p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Control de versiones:</strong> Git, GitHub</p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Metodologias y gestion:</strong> Jira</p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Bases de datos:</strong> MySQL (Workbench, phpMyAdmin), MongoDB (Atlas, Compass)</p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Diseno UX/UI:</strong> Figma, Miro</p>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold text-[rgb(var(--accent-dark))] mb-5">Educacion</h2>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold">SENA</p>
                  <p>Tecnologo en Analisis y Desarrollo de Software</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--gray))]">Bogota - 2022 a 2024</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold">SENA</p>
                  <p>Panificacion</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--gray))]">Bogota - 2020</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold">IED Confederacion Brisas del Diamante</p>
                  <p>Bachiller Academico</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--gray))]">Bogota - 2020</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold">IED Fernando Gonzalez Ochoa</p>
                  <p>Basica Primaria</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--gray))]">Bogota - 2011</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold text-[rgb(var(--accent-dark))] mb-5">Referencias</h2>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold">Familiares</p>
                  <p>Maria Nancy Bernate - Comerciante - 3125817770</p>
                  <p>Nelly Bernate - Empleada - 3143878596</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold">Personales</p>
                  <p>Aldair Devia Lopez - Guarda de seguridad - 3127050270</p>
